No. 120,

Orig.

New Jersey v. New York.

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $255,157.62 for the period May 15 through November 15, 1996, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 517 U. S. 1242.]
